---
---

<section id="experiences" class="py-24 lg:py-32 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-20">
      <div>
        <p class="text-forest-600 text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4">The Lifestyle</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-stone-800 mb-6">
          More Than a Home — <br />A Way of Living
        </h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Living in Nosara means joining a community that values wellness, nature, 
          and authentic connection. From world-class surf to farm-to-table dining, 
          every day offers new ways to engage with this extraordinary place.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="relative">
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507525428034-b723cf961d3e?q=80&w=2073&auto=format&fit=crop"
          alt="Nosara beach at sunset"
          class="w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover rounded-sm"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Experience Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      
      <!-- Surf -->
      <div class="group">
        <div class="img-zoom aspect-square mb-6 rounded-sm">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1502680390469-be75c86b636f?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop"
            alt="Surfing in Nosara"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-stone-800 mb-2">World-Class Surf</h3>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Playa Guiones offers consistent waves year-round, perfect for beginners and experts alike.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Yoga -->
      <div class="group">
        <div class="img-zoom aspect-square mb-6 rounded-sm">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544367567-0f2fcb009e0b?q=80&w=2120&auto=format&fit=crop"
            alt="Yoga retreat"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-stone-800 mb-2">Wellness & Yoga</h3>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Home to renowned yoga retreats and wellness centers focused on mind-body harmony.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Nature -->
      <div class="group">
        <div class="img-zoom aspect-square mb-6 rounded-sm">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1596392927852-2a18c336643e?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop"
            alt="Costa Rica wildlife"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-stone-800 mb-2">Pristine Nature</h3>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Protected wildlife, sea turtle sanctuaries, and untouched tropical forests at your doorstep.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Dining -->
      <div class="group">
        <div class="img-zoom aspect-square mb-6 rounded-sm">
          <img 
            src="/images/hero-1.png"
            alt="Coyol Restaurant - Farm to table dining in Nosara"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-stone-800 mb-2">Farm-to-Table</h3>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          A thriving culinary scene celebrating local ingredients and international flavors.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- Blue Zone Banner -->
<section class="relative py-20 bg-forest-700">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <p class="text-forest-200 text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4">Nicoya Peninsula</p>
    <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-white mb-6">
      One of the World's Five Blue Zones
    </h2>
    <p class="text-forest-100 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      The Nicoya Peninsula is recognized as one of only five Blue Zones on Earth — 
      regions where people live measurably longer, healthier lives. The secret? 
      Community, purpose, natural living, and an abundance of pura vida.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
